{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw two-- two waiters looking at us, and we knew we were caught.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were deciding what we're going to say when they come and all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of them came over and said, oh, you're friends are over in the other-- the other-- in the first class buffet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, come on, I'll show you where they are, and very rude.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- so we thought we'd better go, so we got up to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as we passed down the hallway that connected the two, he said, and that door goes over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think out of somewhere-- somewhere, and went on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't know what he was talking about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a friend there, and-- also from the ambulance corps, so we went back and checked it out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was where the servants from the hotel came in to have their breakfast and so forth in the buffet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we sneaked out through there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As we passed out through the hotel lobby, the concierge said, oh, can I help you?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're-- we're helping ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Quite all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went out and found a-- rented a truck, and so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were on your again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how I got into Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
